In this repository you'll find some working buildroot configurations
to build application-specific intramfs images.

portbouncer
===========
Buildroot configuration for a simple port-forwarding
linux system, meant to be used as a xen-pv system

Should be used as a general buildroot external customization layer
Tested with buildroot-2015.2

The required configuration can by enabled by executing

  $ make BR2_EXTERNAL=<path_to_this_repo> xen-portbouncer_defconfig

